{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"iddb2e9590-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s322"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"322"},"text":"§ 322.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Determination on application","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"In acting upon such applications the Board of Governors of the Federal Reserve System shall consider the financial condition of the applying bank, the general character of its management, and whether or not the corporate powers exercised are consistent with the purposes of this chapter.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"iddb2e9591-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1913-12-23/ch6/s9"},"text":"Dec. 23, 1913, ch. 6, § 9","children":[],"tail":" (par.), as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1917-06-21/ch32/s3"},"text":"June 21, 1917, ch. 32, § 3","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/40/233"},"text":"40 Stat. 233","children":[],"tail":"; amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1935-08-23/ch614"},"text":"Aug. 23, 1935, ch. 614","children":[],"tail":", title II, § 203(a), "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/49/704"},"text":"49 Stat. 704","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"iddb2e9592-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"iddb2e9593-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"iddb2e9594-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"This chapter, referred to in text, was in the original “this Act”, meaning ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1913-12-23/ch6"},"text":"act Dec. 23, 1913, ch. 6","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/38/251"},"text":"38 Stat. 251","children":[],"tail":", known as the Federal Reserve Act. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see References in Text note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s226"},"text":"section 226 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"iddb2e9595-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section is comprised of the fourth par. of section 9 of act ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1913-12-23"},"text":"Dec. 23, 1913","children":[],"tail":", as amended. The fourth par. constituted the second par. of section 9 in 1917 ("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/40/232"},"text":"40 Stat. 232","children":[],"tail":"), became the third par. in 1927 ("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/44/1229"},"text":"44 Stat. 1229","children":[],"tail":"), and became the fourth par. in 1950 ("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/64/458"},"text":"64 Stat. 458","children":[],"tail":"). For further details, see Codification note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s321"},"text":"section 321 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"iddb2e9596-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"changeOfName","id":"iddb2e9597-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Change of Name","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section 203(a) of act ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1935-08-23"},"text":"Aug. 23, 1935","children":[],"tail":", changed name of Federal Reserve Board to Board of Governors of the Federal Reserve System."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
